stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Incomplete: Customer starts checkout
    Incomplete --> Trialing: Initial payment confirmed\n(if trial enabled)
    Incomplete --> Active: Initial payment confirmed\n(no trial)
    Incomplete --> [*]: Payment abandoned

    Trialing --> Active: Trial ends +\npayment succeeds
    Trialing --> Cancelled: Trial ends +\nno payment method

    Active --> PastDue: Payment fails
    Active --> Paused: Customer requests pause
    Active --> Cancelled: Customer cancels\nor admin cancels

    PastDue --> Active: Payment recovered\n(dunning success)
    PastDue --> Cancelled: Dunning exhausted\n(involuntary churn)

    Paused --> Active: Pause period ends\nor customer resumes
    Paused --> Cancelled: Customer cancels\nwhile paused

    Cancelled --> Active: Winback / resubscribe

    note right of Active
        Billing runs automatically
        each cycle (monthly/annual)
    end note

    note right of PastDue
        Grace period applies
        Dunning retries in progress
    end note

    note right of Paused
        No billing during pause
        Access may be restricted
    end note
